snippet.description:
Like ♤ Subscribe ♧ Share ♤ Speak

That either annoying or tantalizing voice that is spread all over this video is using all the content wherein under the fair use doctrine in a transformative manner.

Not great at writing up descriptions but I don't want to giveaway views, word is YouTube's algorithm prefers long and drawn out descriptions but in my experience, the little arrow rarely gets hit. On this channel, you are the prize and reward, this will never be a ft thing but I appreciate you coming through and spending a little bit of your time listening to a moron rant and sometimes ramble about a vast variety of topics, ultimately whatever I think is worth giving a gander.
